    "Further, this classification also has the ability to feed into the development of advanced driver-assistance systems, thereby enabling these systems to better understand and predict human behavior; this may also serve to prevent accidents.In this context, the review presented in [23] offers an inclusive framework that addresses the regulation of autonomous vehicles and associated challenges, both in the United States and Europe.",
    "Regulatory issues, particularly those pertaining to the legal interpretation of driver behavior, present complex problems.",
